{"tid":2497071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"機智號直升機在火星成功試飛　人造飛行器首次太空飛行","createTime":"2021-04-20T09:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:35:16.000Z","uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e44c821fb2e8518c0e3f0b7237c1551e00db3609","tid":2497071,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"美國太空總署火星探測器「毅力號」搭載的「機智號」直升機，在火星表面首次試飛成功。「毅力號」傳回的片段顯示，重1.8公斤的「機智號」直升機，在火星表面垂直上升3米後，執行了懸停、下降和著陸等所有設定動作，全程歷時39秒。美國太空總署宣布，「機智號」已完成首次飛行，是一架動力飛行器在另一個星球的首次飛行。 按照計劃，「機智號」將在火星上進行5次飛行，希望對火星的特殊地形進行更近距離觀察。「機智號」原定在本月11日首飛，但進行旋翼高轉速測試時發現潛在問題，因而押後試飛。 由於火星大氣極為稀薄，氣壓不及地球的1%，因此「機智號」要在火星上起飛，就如同在地球上數千米的高空飛行一樣，特別設計的旋翼轉速要高達每分鐘2400轉才能起飛。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p1KolyCqICI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp1KolyCqICI&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=af5c5272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p1KolyCqICI</a>"},{"pid":"ca33e5807ea22f87d713cd4192674c9e126390a3","tid":2497071,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387944/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%99%BA%E8%99%9F%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%A9%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%81%AB%E6%98%9F%E9%A6%96%E9%A3%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2387944%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%2598%259F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=63a850d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2387944/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%99%BA%E8%99%9F%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%A9%9F%E5%9C%A8%E7%81%AB%E6%98%9F%E9%A6%96%E9%A3%9B%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F</a>"},{"pid":"695afb84d90dfb12c7aa5dd9a4e71108ab2f7368","tid":2497071,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"有幾難？"},{"pid":"cfdbd9641fd2beb6c1a02a13c571ac34d41f2e47","tid":2497071,"uid":235853,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"695afb84d90dfb12c7aa5dd9a4e71108ab2f7368","tid":2497071,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"有幾難？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於火星大氣極為稀薄，氣壓不及地球的1%，因此「機智號」要在火星上起飛，就如同在地球上數千米的高空飛行一樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n提提你幾年前鄰國仲掙扎緊整一部可以喺高原上用嘅引擎"},{"pid":"9164e7a8d6437dfdb5f7ba6d1a8f5167b36bbe8e","tid":2497071,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"地球到火星的平均距離為5,460 萬公里，所以光從地球到火星單趟要3 分2 秒，來回一趟就是6 分4 秒。<br />\n<br />\n即係<br />\n1. 無人駕駛<br />\n2. 無法即時遙控"},{"pid":"4932b5454f80aca28c9b5462cdf840bbd19f5231","tid":2497071,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"695afb84d90dfb12c7aa5dd9a4e71108ab2f7368","tid":2497071,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"有幾難？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:22:06.000Z","msg":".................<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dc452e674ab1b17d8c46528e3d208b94a5cac8","tid":2497071,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"695afb84d90dfb12c7aa5dd9a4e71108ab2f7368","tid":2497071,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"有幾難？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"Attention whore<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29103f74b51a8ed05d72875eea4d904b1d029e2b","tid":2497071,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42dc452e674ab1b17d8c46528e3d208b94a5cac8","tid":2497071,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,